headline: Gas and Liquid Handling Stocks Q3 Earnings: IDEX (NYSE:IEX) Best of the Bunch
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q3. Today, we are looking at gas and liquid handling stocks, starting with IDEX (NYSE:IEX).
